# Important title

## Less important title

```catala-metadata
declaration scope S:
  input i content integer
  output r content integer

scope S:
  definition r equals
    if 42 > 42 then
      -i
    else
      i

#[test]
declaration scope T:
  output result content integer

scope T:
  definition result equals (output of S with { -- i : 123 }).r
```

